@startuml
[*] --> LoggedIn
LoggedIn -> Teacher : Continue as teacher
LoggedIn -> Student : Continue as student

Teacher:
    Teacher -> CreateQuiz : New Quiz
    CreateQuiz -> SaveDraft : Draft
    CreateQuiz -> PostQuiz : Publish
    PostQuiz --> ViewResults : Results
    ViewResults --> [*]

Student:
    Student -> SelectQuiz : Choose Quiz
    SelectQuiz -> AnsweringQuiz : Start
    AnsweringQuiz -> SubmitQuiz : Submit
    SubmitQuiz --> ViewResults : Results
    ViewResults --> [*]
@enduml
